steps.instruction:
Recipe from [Alfia Muzio](https://www.bonappetit.com/recipe/fresh-tomato-pizza-sauce)

### Prep
- Drain the tomatoes
- Drain the anchovy fillets from the oil

### Steps
1. Pulse tomatoes, anchovies, garlic, oil, and basil in a food processor or blender until mostly smooth (some texture is okay)
2. season with salt and pepper
